## Environment Configuration

Edit `tests/ui/config/env.ts` to change the base URL or credentials:

```typescript
export const ENV = {
  BASE_URL: 'https://test.com',
  LOGIN_EMAIL: 'test123@gmail.com',
  LOGIN_PASSWORD: 'your-password-here',
  API_BASE_URL: 'https://test.com/api',
};
```

